headline: Cracker Barrel co-founder, 93, blasts $7M/year CEO’s ‘pitiful’ rebrand fail, work with Taco Bell. Is that unfair?
summary: He built the first Cracker Barrel in 1969. Now he says its future is at risk under new leadership.
